@@ -2999,3 +3014,4 @@ git commit -m "feat: add project CLAUDE.md with testing and architecture notes"
 - Monitor position caching for reconnection (30-minute TTL per spec) — deferred to follow-up.
 - Grid reconfiguration proportional mapping at runtime — deferred to follow-up (settings changes take effect on extension restart for v1). The prefs UI writes to GSettings immediately, but the extension does not listen for grid dimension changes at runtime.
 - GSettings enum validation for `placement-mode` and `shelf-edge` — keys use plain `type="s"` (string) for simplicity. Enum validation can be added in a follow-up by switching to GSettings enum types and using `get_enum()`/`set_enum()` in both the extension and prefs UI.
+- Tiled window state preservation through auto-shrink/restore cycle — spec requires restoring tiled position/size, but `WindowScaleState` does not track tile state. A follow-up should add `previousTileMode` tracking.
